FocusPomo Privacy
For us and some of our business partners, our "Privacy Policy" explains the collection, use, sharing, and protection of information related to our mobile services, websites, any software offered on or in connection with the FocusPomo services (collectively referred to as the "Services"), as well as your choices regarding the collection and use of your information.
Welcome to FocusPomo. FocusPomo is a time management software based on the Pomodoro Technique, designed to help users better utilize their time and overcome procrastination.
By using our "Services," you understand and agree that we provide software for you to frame your photos through the relevant "Services."
We collect the following types of information:
Information you provide to us directly:
Analytical Information
:
We use third-party analytics tools to help us measure traffic and usage trends for the "Services." These tools collect information sent by your device or our "Services," including the pages you visit, add-ons, and other information that assists us in improving the "Services." We collect this information and use it alongside analytical data from other users, ensuring it cannot be used to identify any specific individual user.
Device Identifiers
:
When you use a mobile device (such as a tablet or phone) to access our "Services," we may perform access, collection, monitoring, storage operations on your device, and/or remotely store one or more "Device Identifiers." Device Identifiers are small data files or similar data structures stored on or associated with your mobile device, serving as your device's unique identifier. Device Identifiers may involve data stored in connection with the device hardware, data stored in connection with the device's operating system or other software, or data sent to the device by LATTE.
Device Identifiers can provide us or our third-party partners with information about how you browse and use the "Services" and assist us or others in providing reports. If the use or availability of Device Identifiers is impaired or disabled, certain features of the "Services" may not function properly.
Health Data
Our application utilizes Apple's APIs to interact with the Apple Health app on your device for the purpose of accessing specific health-related data ("Health Data"). This includes data such as:
Duration of Mindfulness Practices
We firmly commit to not utilizing your Health Data for purposes like marketing, advertising, or usage-based data mining. Access to your Health Data is executed solely through Apple Health on a local basis, ensuring that the app neither stores nor caches this information. All processing of your Health Data is confined to your device, guaranteeing that it is not transmitted to any external servers. Please be aware that our app requires your explicit permission to access or input data into Apple Health.
In addition to specific uses of information described in this "Privacy Policy," we may use the information we receive for:
Developing and testing new products and features.
Diagnosing or resolving technical issues.
Unless stated in this "Policy," we will not lend or sell your information to third parties outside of FocusPomo (or the corporate group to which FocusPomo belongs) without your consent.
Parties with whom we may share your information:
We may also share your information with third-party organizations (hereinafter referred to as "Service Providers") that assist us in providing the "Services," along with information about tools such as cookies, log files, Device Identifiers, and location data. Our "Service Providers" will have the right to access your information as necessary and provide the "Services" under reasonable confidentiality terms.
We will remove identifiable data about you and share anonymous data with others. We may also combine your information with other information in a manner that is no longer associated with you and share that aggregated information.
We are not responsible for the actions of any websites or services linked to our "Services," including the information or content provided by such websites and services. Please remember that when you use a link to go from our "Services" to other websites or services, our "Privacy Policy" does not apply to those third-party websites or services. Your browsing and interaction on any third-party website or service, including those with links on our website, are subject to that third party's own rules and policies. Furthermore, we are not responsible and have no control over any third party that you authorize to access your "User Content." You bear all risks associated with using a third-party website or service that has access to your "User Content."
If you have any questions about this "Privacy Policy" or the "Services," please contact us:
amazingwork@126.com
FocusPomo may modify or update this "Privacy Policy" from time to time, so please review it periodically. We may provide additional forms of notice of modifications or updates as appropriate under the circumstances. Your continued use of FocusPomo or the "Services" after any modification to this "Privacy Policy" will constitute your acceptance of such modification.
